<!-- Seção: A Dor que Resolvemos -->
<section id="proposito" class="py-32 px-6 lg:px-12 relative z-10 pointer-events-auto bg-[#06080D] scroll-mt-28">
    <!-- Background Glow Effect -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute left-1/4 top-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-red-500/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] mix-blend-screen"></div>
        <div class="absolute right-1/4 bottom-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#00E5FF]/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] mix-blend-screen"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tighter mb-6" data-translate="prob-title">
                O Fim da <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 via-orange-400 to-yellow-500">Exaustão</span> Humana.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed" data-translate="prob-subtitle">
                Não projetamos robôs para substituir as pessoas, mas sim para amplificar o potencial humano. O mundo enfrenta uma crise silenciosa, e nós somos a resposta definitiva.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            <!-- Esgotamento Humano -->
            <div data-tilt data-tilt-max="5" data-tilt-speed="400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-500 transform-gpu overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl" style="transform-style: preserve-3d;">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-red-500 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-red-500/20 group-hover:bg-red-500/20 transition-colors" style="transform: translateZ(30px);">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight" style="transform: translateZ(20px);" data-translate="prob-card1-title">Esgotamento Crônico</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="transform: translateZ(10px);" data-translate="prob-card1-desc">
                    Pessoas destruindo a saúde física e mental com tarefas repetitivas e insalubres. Os robôs Zetta assumem o fardo pesado para que humanos foquem na criatividade e gestão.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Escassez de Mão de Obra -->
            <div data-tilt data-tilt-max="5" data-tilt-speed="400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-[#00E5FF]/30 transition-all duration-500 transform-gpu overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl" style="transform-style: preserve-3d;">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#00E5FF] to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#00E5FF]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-[#00E5FF]/20 group-hover:bg-[#00E5FF]/20 transition-colors" style="transform: translateZ(30px);">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#00E5FF]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight" style="transform: translateZ(20px);" data-translate="prob-card2-title">Escassez de Operação</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="transform: translateZ(10px);" data-translate="prob-card2-desc">
                    Indústrias paralisadas por falta de mão de obra. Da logística de almoxarifado à higienização hospitalar crítica e rondas noturnas 24/7, nós preenchemos as lacunas críticas.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Sobrecarga no Lar/Agro -->
            <div data-tilt data-tilt-max="5" data-tilt-speed="400" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" class="group relative p-10 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all duration-500 transform-gpu overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl shadow-2xl" style="transform-style: preserve-3d;">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-green-500 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-8 border border-green-500/20 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors" style="transform: translateZ(30px);">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight" style="transform: translateZ(20px);" data-translate="prob-card3-title">Sobrecarga Doméstica e Agro</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="transform: translateZ(10px);" data-translate="prob-card3-desc">
                    Famílias sem tempo livre e pequenos agricultores perdendo colheitas. Levamos eficiência empática para dentro de casa e precisão sustentável para a lavoura.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
